  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The population of a town is currently 50,000, and the population is estimated to increase each year by 3% from the previous year. Which of the following equations can be used to estimate the number of years, <span class=\"italic\">t</span>, it will take for the population of the town to reach 60,000 ?</p>\n",
